      when "5-2-3-A-b-p"
        | Verbs with a specific verbal noun:
      when "5-2-3-B-p"
        | When verbs have a short vowel in the root, the vowel is left unlengthened before #[i -t], e.g., #[i nitear], #[i niteá], #[i nite], but #[i ním], #[i níodh], #[i nífí], etc. However, #[i léigh] etc. have long vowels throughout, e.g., #[i léitear], #[i léiteá], #[i léite].
